        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 9, "name": "Yext" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 10, "name": "Moz Local" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the best SEO tool for a dental practice in 2026?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "It depends on the gap. For map-pack and \"dentist near me\" rankings, Google Business Profile (free) + BrightLocal ($39/mo). For patient review velocity, Birdeye. For ongoing content (the most common gap), theStacc at $99/mo publishes dental articles and posts to GBP automatically." }},
