        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What dental keywords should I target first?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Start with high-intent local terms: \"dentist near me\", \"dentist [your city]\", \"emergency dentist [your city]\", \"Invisalign [your city]\". Then expand to informational queries: \"how much does Invisalign cost\", \"is root canal painful\", \"how often should I see a dentist\"." }},
