        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Should I hire a dental marketing agency or DIY?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "DIY works if you can spare 6 to 10 hours a week. Most owner-dentists cannot — that hour is worth $300 to $700 in chair time. A managed content service like theStacc at $99/mo replaces both an agency and the time cost." }}
