          <li><strong>Insurance search</strong> — "dentist that takes [insurer] [city]". Decided by service pages that list accepted plans.</li>
          <li><strong>New-patient research</strong> — "best family dentist [neighborhood]". Decided by reviews + a credibility-rich website.</li>
